## Deploying
You can deploy StudyNotion using:
- Docker: Provide Dockerfile and docker-compose (service: web, db)
- Cloud platforms: Vercel for frontend (Next.js), Render/Heroku/DigitalOcean for backend
- Kubernetes: Create manifests/Helm charts for production environments

Add CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions) to run tests, lint, and deploy.

