## Roadmap / Ideas
- Improve accessibility and mobile UX
- Add SCORM/LTI support for LMS integration
- Expand analytics and instructor reporting
- Add multi-tenant support and white-labeling
- Improve localization / i18n

## Troubleshooting
- Common issues:
  - "Cannot connect to DB": check MONGO_URI/DATABASE_URL and ensure database is running and accessible.
  - "Stripe webhook failed": verify webhook signing secret and endpoint configuration.
  - "CORS errors": check server CORS settings and client API URL.

